---
title: Middle Eastern Spiced Turkey Mince with courgette, couscous and Greek style cheese
description: Charred courgette and tangy Greek style cheese garnish a spiced Turkey stew in this warm and hearty dish filled with flavour and fun.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R05_W07_IE_IEXCFT18822-2_Main_high-187ab03e.jpg
